      <h2 class="en-serif" style="margin: 0; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(27px,2.4vw+16px,38px); line-height: 1.2; color: #f3efe9;">She keeps your readings.</h2>
      <p style="margin: 16px auto 0; font-size: clamp(15px,0.4vw+14px,17px); line-height: 1.6; color: #9aa0c2; max-width: 440px; text-wrap: pretty;">Ask a real question, draw your own cards, and let Enchantra hold the thread so you can watch it unfold. Join the waitlist for early access.</p>
